This Privacy Policy explains how the mobile game Numeralea ("the Game", "we", "us") handles your information. We have designed the Game to collect as little data as possible.

1. Information we collect
We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal information to our own servers. The Game has no developer account system, no analytics, and no advertising.

All of your game data — progress, unlocks, achievements, scores, settings, and the in‑game encyclopedia — is stored only locally on your device. We have no access to it.

2. Game Center (optional)
If you are signed in to Apple Game Center, the Game may submit your achievements and scores to Game Center so they appear on your Game Center profile and leaderboards. This feature is optional — you can decline the Game Center sign‑in prompt and the Game will work fully offline.

Game Center is operated by Apple. Any data handled through Game Center is governed by Apple's Privacy Policy. We do not receive your Apple ID, name, email, or any other personal identifier from Game Center.

3. Network use
The Game functions fully offline. A network connection is used only to communicate with Apple Game Center (when you are signed in). The Game does not contact any other server.

4. Third parties
The Game contains no third‑party advertising, analytics, tracking, or social SDKs. We do not sell or share any data, because we do not collect any.

5. Children's privacy
The Game does not knowingly collect any personal information from anyone, including children. Because no personal data is collected, the Game is suitable for all ages with respect to data privacy.

6. Data retention & deletion
Local game data remains on your device until you delete it. Deleting the Game removes all locally stored data. Achievement/score data already submitted to Game Center is managed by Apple and can be removed through your Game Center / Apple ID settings.

7. Changes to this policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date above reflects the latest version.

8. Contact
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at: guzhoudiaoxue@outlook.com

隐私政策 — 万数归源（Numeralea）
